metadata.name: The Founders
metadata.description:
This piece shows a group of NFT project founders & influencers who have built their fortune on the backs of unsuspecting and trusting investors who see them as the pioneers of the space.

The shady founders are hosting a Twitter Space to address the growing concerns and FUD surrounding their PFP project, answering any questions the buyers may have before they eventually fade into the dark.

The three step plan,  
Mint, Spaces, Rug!

Easiest million of their lives.
